Jynx (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0123: Scyther
Pokémon
#0125: Electabuzz →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Jynx (TCG Pocket).

Jynx has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Jynx cards are normally Psychic-type or Water-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Jynx

Jynx
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
